BLINDNESS

Usage       : cast 'blindness' <victim>
Accumulative: No.
Duration    : 2 + level hours.

Blindness will blind a victim failing its saving throw.  A blinded
person will have -4 penalty to both hitroll and AC.  In addition, blinded
creatures will be unable to manipulate (wear, remove, etc) their objects.

See Also: CURE BLIND
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
